snippet.title: Queen Rules - Introduction Video (In Game)
snippet.description: This entirely original puzzle game invites you to travel through kingdoms. Unique game play and enchanting clay characters challenge you with a puzzle experience like no other. It’s simple to learn and difficult to master, an almost magical combination we think you’ll love.
